{
  "text": "As shown in Fig. 13(a) , the complete mno transformation block translates the three abc voltages into three mno components using (5) and then to the six dq mno components using [CITATION_1] . These voltage components are acted upon by the power controller of Fig. 10 to generate the six dq mno current components references, in order to produce oscillation free active and reactive powers as ordered, following a specific power control strategy (next session).",
